videos.headline: S. Barkley run for 19 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Saquon Barkley run for 19 yds to the PnSt 49 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Ohio State stuffs Penn State's drive with a blocked FG
videos.description: Penn State's promising first drive ends with nothing to show for it when Ohio State blocks the field goal attempt to keep the game scoreless.

videos.headline: S. Barkley run for 27 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Saquon Barkley run for 27 yds to the OhSt 40 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Penn State muffs punt to open the door for Ohio State
videos.description: John Reid muffs the punt for Penn State, allowing Ohio State to recover which the Buckeyes would cash in for a field goal to take a 3-0 lead.

videos.headline: Baugh's nasty spin move gets Ohio State's first TD
videos.description: Marcus Baugh makes the catch and then shakes a defender with a nasty spin move before fighting his way into the end zone to boost Ohio State's lead to 9-0.

videos.headline: J.T. Barrett makes magic, avoids sack, runs for the 1st
videos.description: J.T. Barrett run for 19 yds to the PnSt 32 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: T. McSorley pass,to D. Hamilton for 34 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Trace McSorley pass complete to DaeSean Hamilton for 34 yds to the OhSt 20 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Penn State strikes back just before the half with Godwin TD
videos.description: After struggling offensively for most of the first half, Penn State puts it together when Trace McSorley finds Chris Godwin for a jump ball touchdown with nine seconds remaining in the half.

videos.headline: Penn State Kicker Joey Julius prevents Ohio State from scoring on Kickoff
videos.description: Joey Julius kickoff for 62 yds , Parris Campbell return for 22 yds to the OhSt 25

videos.headline: Samuel breaks free and Penn State has no chance of catching him
videos.description: Curtis Samuel takes the hand off and then takes off, going 74 yards untouched to the house to boost Ohio State's lead to 19-7.

videos.headline: TEAM run for -30 yds for a SAFETY,TEAM fumbled, recovered by PnSt B. Gillikin,for a SAFETY
videos.description: TEAM run for a loss of 30 yards for a SAFETY TEAM fumbled, recovered by PnSt Blake Gillikin for a SAFETY

videos.headline: S. Barkley run for 37 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Saquon Barkley run for 37 yds to the OhSt 37 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: T. McSorley pass,to S. Blacknall for 35 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Trace McSorley pass complete to Saeed Blacknall for 35 yds to the OhSt 2 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: McSorley dives for the pylon to get Penn State back in it
videos.description: Down 14, Trace McSorley scrambles right and makes a dive for the pylon to score and bring Penn State back within a score at 21-14.

videos.headline: Penn State blocks Ohio State punt to keep hopes alive
videos.description: TEAM punt blocked by Cameron Brown blocked by Cameron Brown

videos.headline: Penn State returns blocked FG for stunning upset of Ohio State
videos.description: Ohio State lines up for a 45-yard field goal that gets blocked and run all the way back by Grant Haley to give Penn State the stunning 24-21 lead with just over four minutes left in the game.

videos.headline: Penn State comes up big with 3rd down sack
videos.description: J.T. Barrett sacked by Jason Cabinda for a loss of 13 yards to the OhSt 29

videos.headline: Ohio State sacked on crucial 4th down
videos.description: J.T. Barrett sacked by Evan Schwan and Kevin Givens for a loss of 6 yards to the OhSt 23

videos.headline: Meyer says Ohio State 'not a great team right now'
videos.description: Urban Meyer breaks down what went wrong for Ohio State against Penn State.
